State.Author: ModdingLinked
State.Description: A (third party) fork of Mod Organizer 2 bringing a series of improvements and preventing common annoyances.
State.Name: Mod Organizer 2 - ModdingLinked Edition

State.Author: Kezyma
State.Description: Root Builder is a Mod Organizer 2 plugin that allows you to manage files in the base game folder through Mod Organizer, leaving your game folder in pristine, vanilla condition!
State.Name: Kezyma's Root Builder for Mod Organizer

State.Author: hadesTTW
State.Description: A simple mod that removes the scanlines, the dirt, and the distortion of the Pip-Boy screen, and makes the background solid black. Compatible with multiple alternate Pip-Boys and Darnified UI out of the box.
State.Name: Clean Pip-Boy 2022

State.Author: Roy Batty - LuthienAnarion
State.Description: Simple patcher to make Fallout New Vegas 4GB Aware. Supports all known Steam and GoG versions. The EPIC Games, Bethesda.net and XBOX Game pass versions are NOT supported since NVSE will not support them either.
State.Name: FNV 4GB Patcher

State.Author: lStewieAl
State.Description: Fixes a save bloating issue related to actors detecting the player, improving save/load speed and decreasing save size 10-30% depending on playthrough length.
State.Name: ActorCause Save Bloat Fix

Original.Name: DSOAL - True 3D Sound for Headphones (HRTF mod) v1.4-65094-v1-4-1667751016.zip

State.Author: kcat
State.Description: Enables 3D positional audio in Fallout: New Vegas or any other game that supports DirectSound3D. You'll be able to hear if sounds are in front, behind, above, or below you in a full 360 degrees. Optionally, you can use this mod to enable up to 7.0 speakers, 3rd order Ambisonics, or up to EAX 4.0 in other compatible games.
State.Name: DSOAL - True 3D Sound for Headphones (HRTF mod) v1.4

State.Author: BmanBlazer
State.Description: This mod is designed to update the HUD for 1080p resolutions or higher (1440p, 4K, etc) while maintaining the same original look and style.
State.Name: Vanilla HUD Remastered (4K)

State.Author: Queue
State.Description: Implements structured exception handling and sanity checking to reduce frequency of game crashes.
State.Name: NVAC - New Vegas Anti Crash

State.Author: chilloucik
State.Description: A simple HD upscale of all world maps.
State.Name: World Map HD

State.Author: lStewieAl
State.Description: Improves framerate in combat by fixing an engine bug that lowered framerate while attacking an enemy with a health-bar visible.
State.Name: Combat Lag Fix (NVSE)
